BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260718
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260719
SUMMARY:Day 13: Blind Channel → Squirrel Cove (Cortes Island)
LOCATION:Squirrel Cove\, Cortes Island
DESCRIPTION:37 NM · ~3.7 hrs\nOvernight: Squirrel Cove\, Cortes Island\n\nNote: Gentle re-entry to the southern waters. The lagoon inside Squirrel Cove is one of those hidden BC gems — explore it by kayak or dinghy at high tide.
URL:https://troyh.github.io/TravelItinerary/?i=2026%20Summer%20Cruise&day=13
UID:day-13-20260718@travelitinerary
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260719
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260720
SUMMARY:Day 14: Squirrel Cove → Montague Harbour (Galiano Island)
LOCATION:Montague Harbour Marine Provincial Park\, Galiano Island
DESCRIPTION:98.9 NM · ~6.6 hrs\nOvernight: Montague Harbour Marine Provincial Park\, Galiano Island\n\nNote: Active Pass: narrow channel between Galiano and Mayne Islands with heavy BC Ferries traffic. Reduce speed\, hug the correct side\, and give ferries wide berth.
URL:https://troyh.github.io/TravelItinerary/?i=2026%20Summer%20Cruise&day=14
UID:day-14-20260719@travelitinerary
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260720
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260721
SUMMARY:Day 15: Gulf Islands — Layover
LOCATION:Montague Harbour or Dionisio Point\, Galiano Island
DESCRIPTION:Overnight: Montague Harbour or Dionisio Point\, Galiano Island\n\nNote: First full Gulf Islands decompression day. No agenda required.
URL:https://troyh.github.io/TravelItinerary/?i=2026%20Summer%20Cruise&day=15
UID:day-15-20260720@travelitinerary
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260721
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260722
SUMMARY:Day 16: Gulf Islands — Layover
LOCATION:Prevost Island\, Wallace Island\, or Ganges Harbour (Salt Spring)
DESCRIPTION:Overnight: Prevost Island\, Wallace Island\, or Ganges Harbour (Salt Spring)\n\nNote: Second Gulf Islands layover. No agenda — use it however the family wants. Salt Spring Ganges is excellent if anyone wants shops or a proper meal ashore.
URL:https://troyh.github.io/TravelItinerary/?i=2026%20Summer%20Cruise&day=16
UID:day-16-20260721@travelitinerary
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260722
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260723
SUMMARY:Day 17: Gulf Islands → Victoria (fuel) → Seattle
LOCATION:Home Marina\, Seattle
DESCRIPTION:90 NM · ~4.5 hrs\nOvernight: Home Marina\, Seattle\n\nNote: Slightly over the usual 100 NM preference\, but Victoria breaks it naturally into two segments. Register everyone on the CBP ROAM app before leaving Victoria. Shilshole or Lake Union via the locks for Seattle landfall.
URL:https://troyh.github.io/TravelItinerary/?i=2026%20Summer%20Cruise&day=17
UID:day-17-20260722@travelitinerary
END:VEVENT
